==Indonesian==
===Etymology===
From English ''[[homosexuality]]''.

===Noun===
'''homosex'''
# [[homosexuality]]

===Adjective===
'''homosex'''
# Of, relating to, or having a sexual orientation to persons of the same sex.

====Usage note====
'''orang homosex'''
# homosexual people

